# HS Branding

Always follow `BRANDING.md` and `src/styles/branding.ts`.

- Use CSS tokens: `bg-surface`, `text-secondary`, `accent`, `border-border` — never hardcode Starlink blue or raw hex in components.
- Cards: `rounded-[20px]`, border `border-border`, background `bg-surface`.
- Labels: class `grok-label` (uppercase, tracked).
- Buttons: pill shape, primary = `bg-accent text-background`.
- Background: `grok-bg` on full-page layouts.
- Motion: 200ms, subtle press scale only.

Import tokens when needed: `import { brand, habitLawColors } from "@/styles/branding"`.
